OL,3,CITV Central wins Royal Television
OL,4,CSociety award for Nottingham Attacks
OL,5,Ccoverage
OL,7,FITV News Central is celebrating
OL,8,Fsuccess after winning a Royal
OL,9,FTelevision Society award for coverage
OL,10,Fon the day of the Nottingham attacks.
OL,12,FThe team won the Nations and Regions
OL,13,FNews Award for its 6pm programme
OL,14,Fbroadcast on the day of the attacks
OL,15,F(13 June 2023), live from locations
OL,16,Facross Nottingham.
OL,18,FThe judges said; "This was a hotly
OL,19,Fcontested category with a number of
OL,20,Fspecial themed programmes praised by
OL,21,Fjurors.
