OL,3,CITV Central wins Royal Television
OL,4,CSociety award for Nottingham Attacks
OL,5,Ccoverage
OL,7,F"The winner stood out for the
OL,8,Foutstanding way that the team dealt
OL,9,Fwith the pressures of a major breaking
OL,10,Fstory, obviously rooted in the local
OL,11,Fcommunity and covering all the angles."
OL,13,FLiz Hannam, Head of News for ITV News
OL,14,FCentral said; "The attacks had a
OL,15,Fdevastating impact on the city of
OL,16,FNottingham and as the local
OL,17,Fbroadcaster we felt the full weight of
OL,18,Fresponsibility to tell the story in as
OL,19,Fsensitive a manner as possible while
OL,20,Fshowing the true horror of what had
OL,21,Fhappened.
