OL,7,F"So it is reassuring to have
OL,8,Frecognition from the national RTS that
OL,9,Fwe did the job well. And I want to
OL,10,Fthank our viewers who let us into
OL,11,Ftheir homes every night and trust us
OL,12,Fto provide accurate news in an
OL,13,Fincreasingly divided world."
